name: infodatahouse.net
overview:
Infodatahouse 2013 conference held at Grand Royale Hotel, Binghmaton, New York, the summit focuses on networking, big data analytics and data pipeline. The meetup aims to talk about the revolutionary data mining. It will cater to all aspects from data acquisition to data visualization. The meetup talks about leveraging data providing opportunities for start ups.

The conference agenda is to provide information about data analytics fundamentals. The new funding trends, business opportunities and new products will be discussed for growing businesses.

The meetup caters to layman and no technical knowledge is required. Anyone interested in the revolutionary data analytics, predictive analytics and big data can be a part of this summit.

Predictive analytics and big data analytics are the key factors to be discussed in the meetup. Visual analytics and forecasting benefits are showcased for the audience to know about data analytics.
